article.headline: Ark.-Little Rock 58, North Texas 54
article.story: DENTON, Texas -- John Fowler scored 13 points and got nine rebounds as Arkansas-Little Rock beat North Texas 58-54 on Saturday night. Also scoring in the double digits for Arkansas-Little Rock (20-7, 13-3 Sun Belt) were Shane Edwards with 12 and Wayne Burton with 10. Adam McCoy scored 15 for North Texas (16-11, 9-7). Eric Tramiel scored 13 and Collin Dennis had 12. Arkansas-Little Rock led 26-24 at the half. Arkansas-Little Rock shot 37 percent from the field while North Texas shot 25 percent.
